# startLoading()

**Instance Method**

Starts protocol-specific loading of the request.

## Declaration

```swift
func startLoading()
```

## Discussion

When this method is called, the subclass implementation should start loading the request, providing feedback to the URL loading system via the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/URLProtocolClient] protocol.

Subclasses must implement this method.

## Starting and stopping downloads

- **stopLoading()**: Stops protocol-specific loading of the request.
